---
title: Chilli Beef Rump Noodles with bell peppers and scattered scallions
description: These sweet chilli beef strip noodles are salty, sweet, and just a little bit spicy. The sprinkling of scallions adds crunch and a bit of brightness while the fried veg gets you one step closer to that all-important five-a-day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R14_W15_IE_IEQCLB13679-3_Main_R_high-5a2ec686.jpg
